        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6494",
        "content": "So they mounted and pursued them, some taking the eastern pass and others that which led to the Wady of Emmets, nor was it long before the apes came in sight of the fugitives, as they were about to enter the valley, and hastened after them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
